I know you won’t see this but I have a way to help train bunny which worked for my dog (he failed dog school).
What I do to make him sit and lay down I put my hand to the floor and click while saying the dogs name. I did this and he learnt it in less then a week. Also, after every time he did it right I gave him a treat while he was first learning to tell the dog that following the instructions is good and you get rewarded.

This is just a simple training idea.
I’m a 10 year old girl that had to do this all by herself and it worked!
Again I know you won’t see this, so if people can help Jenna notice this please do.

If bunny isn’t trained try these tricks to get her started.

Thankyou,
Fan.

Fin.
